---
---

<section class="services">
  <div class="container">

    <p class="services__eyebrow">What We Offer</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Academic Support For Every Level</h2>
    <hr class="gold-line" />
    <p class="section-subtitle">Whether you are in high school, college, or pursuing a PhD — we have expert writers and researchers ready to help you succeed.</p>

    <div class="services__grid">

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card__icon">✍️</div>
        <h3>Essay & Assignment Help</h3>
        <p>Professional essay writing and assignment support for high school and college students across all subjects.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>All subjects covered</li>
          <li>Any deadline met</li>
          <li>Plagiarism free</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services" class="service-card__link">Learn More →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card__icon">🔬</div>
        <h3>Research Paper Writing</h3>
        <p>In-depth research papers and reports written by subject matter experts with access to academic databases.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Proper citations & referencing</li>
          <li>All citation styles</li>
          <li>Primary & secondary research</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services" class="service-card__link">Learn More →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card service-card--featured">
        <div class="service-card__badge">Most Popular</div>
        <div class="service-card__icon">🎓</div>
        <h3>Dissertation & Thesis Support</h3>
        <p>Comprehensive dissertation and thesis support for Masters and PhD students from proposal to final defence.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Chapter by chapter support</li>
          <li>Research methodology guidance</li>
          <li>Statistical analysis help</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services" class="service-card__link">Learn More →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card__icon">📝</div>
        <h3>Editing & Proofreading</h3>
        <p>Professional editing and proofreading to polish your work to the highest academic standard.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Grammar & style correction</li>
          <li>Structure & flow improvement</li>
          <li>Formatting & referencing</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services" class="service-card__link">Learn More →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card__icon">📚</div>
        <h3>Homework Assistance</h3>
        <p>Quick and reliable homework help for high school students across all subjects and grade levels.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Math, Science, English</li>
          <li>History & Social Studies</li>
          <li>Fast turnaround</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services" class="service-card__link">Learn More →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card__icon">💡</div>
        <h3>Research Consulting</h3>
        <p>Expert one-on-one consulting for researchers who need guidance on methodology, analysis, and academic writing.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>1-on-1 expert sessions</li>
          <li>Research design support</li>
          <li>Data analysis guidance</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services" class="service-card__link">Learn More →</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="services__cta">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a Free Consultation</a>
      <a href="/services" class="btn-outline">View All Services</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.services {
  padding: var(--section-padding);
  background-color: var(--off-white);
}

.services__eyebrow {
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.services__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.service-card {
  background-color: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 2rem;
  position: relative;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.service-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(27,42,74,0.12);
  border-color: var(--gold);
}

.service-card--featured {
  border-color: var(--gold);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #243558 100%);
}

.service-card--featured h3 {
  color: var(--white);
}

.service-card--featured p {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
}

.service-card--featured ul li {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
}

.service-card--featured .service-card__link {
  color: var(--gold);
}

.service-card__badge {
  position: absolute;
  top: -12px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  background-color: var(--gold);
  color: var(--navy);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 20px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.service-card__icon {
  font-size: 2rem;
}

.service-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: var(--navy);
}

.service-card p {
  color: var(--text-mid);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  flex: 1;
}

.service-card ul {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.4rem;
}

.service-card ul li {
  color: var(--text-mid);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  padding-left: 1rem;
  position: relative;
}

.service-card ul li::before {
  content: '✓';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.service-card__link {
  color: var(--navy);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: color 0.3s ease;
  margin-top: auto;
}

.service-card__link:hover {
  color: var(--gold);
}

.services__cta {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.btn-outline {
  display: inline-block;
  background-color: transparent;
  color: var(--navy);
  padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  border: 2px solid var(--navy);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.btn-outline:hover {
  background-color: var(--navy);
  color: var(--white);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .services__grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

@media (max-width: 580px) {
  .services__grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
</style>